2005-12-30 Version 0.0.5-svn
	   Fabrizio Tarizzo <software@fabriziotarizzo.org>

	* Log messages in a different window (the properties dialog
	  was too small).
	    o configure.ac (new version number)
	    o src/torapplet0.glade (new dialog)
	    o src/torapplet0.glade.c (new labels)
	    o src/torapplet0.py.in (new dialog management, added datetime
	      column)
	    o po/torapplet0.pot (New labels translations)
	    o po/it.po (New labels translated)
	    o po/it.gmo (New labels translated)
	    
2005-12-29 Version 0.0.4-svn
	   Fabrizio Tarizzo <software.fabriziotarizzo.org>

	* src/torapplet0.py.in: Log messages in time order (more recent
	  first), error level displayed as icon instead of text, smaller
	  font.

2005-12-27 Version 0.0.4-svn
	   Fabrizio Tarizzo <software.fabriziotarizzo.org>

	* Added log messages display
	    o configure.ac (New version number)
	    o src/torapplet0.glade (New tab in gtk.Notebook)
	    o src/torapplet0.glade.c (New labels)
	    o src/torapplet0.py.in (gtk.ListStore and gtk.TreeView objects
	    	for log messages)
	    o po/torapplet0.pot (New labels translations)
	    o po/it.po (New labels translated)
	    o po/it.gmo (New labels translated)

2005-12-20 Features of version 0.0.3-svn

	* Visual display of the Tor daemon status (red icon: stopped,
	  green icon: started, dark green icon: sending/receiving);
	* Tooltip with basic informations (daemon status, uptime, 
	  version, bytes sent/received, log warinigs/errors,
	  number of connected onion routers);
	* Menu that allow to start, stop and restart the daemon, and
	  to display an about box and a properties dialog;
	* Properties dialog with informations about daemon activity;
	* GUI for tor-resolve;
	* Support for localization;
	* Italian translation.
